data.description: Investors take notice... This home has so many possibilities having 4 bedrooms 1.5 baths, large living room & an updated kitchen. Expand those possibilities with the second living space which offers a living room & bedroom as well as a common area to share the laundry room area. You will love the newer stainless appliances. The double built in oven is perfect for family gatherings. Classy is what comes to mind with the newer gas cooktop which includes a new vent hood. Owner says that new Double door , pull out freezer drawer, refrigerator conveys with the home! The kitchen updates were completed in 2019 which included New flooring, counter tops, brick backsplash,  appliances & garbage disposal, In 2016 New vinyl double windows, new exterior back doors as well as vinyl siding was added. The 2 car carport as an attached tool room that comes with electric. You will love the large backyard. This home sits on a corner lot....come make it yours.
